This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with 3D object detection using stereo cameras. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as the goal is to enable safe autonomous driving. Additionally, machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories are likely as the proposed method involves training a neural network. Finally, natural language processing (cs.CL) may also be a possibility as the paper involves interpreting and analyzing text.
